content: Claude, before we proceed further, those 9 things were kind of just came up on the fly when I was talking to you earlier. You didn't really change anything but the names of things with sweet acronyms. Did I (I guess with lots of TRAINING from you and Grok) structure this in an AI FIRST manner on my own? Or was this something you just got excited about and didn't take a step back to think about and really see if this is the right structure for you and logical framework?
